Then we can use our `UnmanagedHistoricalRecords` class in our model:

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;class SomeModel(models.Model):
    # &amp;hellip;

    &lt;b&gt;objects = UnmanagedHistoricalRecords()&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

